        '\x20OR\x20',
        'Filter\x20Preview:\x20',
        'Toggle\x20this\x20on\x20to\x20give\x20the\x20profile\x20its\x20own\x20date\x20range.\x20When\x20enabled,\x20the\x20main\x20Forecast\x20date\x20picker\x20disappears\x20and\x20is\x20replaced\x20by\x20the\x20profile\x27s\x20own\x20target\x20week\x20and\x20day\x20selection\x20—\x20so\x20you\x20always\x20know\x20exactly\x20what\x20dates\x20the\x20profile\x20will\x20search.',
        'Visual\x20vs\x20Text:\x20',
        'Hides\x20all\x20PMs\x20so\x20you\x20can\x20focus\x20on\x20corrective\x20and\x20other\x20work\x20order\x20types,\x20any\x20WO\x20with\x20no\x20PM\x20Due\x20Date.',
        'The\x20filter\x20works\x20on\x20results\x20already\x20in\x20the\x20grid\x20—\x20it\x27s\x20instant\x20and\x20doesn\x27t\x20trigger\x20a\x20new\x20MADDON\x20query.',
